dataset_1 <- df_cleaned %>% 
  select(pop2010to2002_rel, #   (   )
         Census2002,        # initial population size
         clo,               # closeness centrality (   )
         clo_w,             #  closeness centrality (   )
         clo_CL6,           # closeness centrality (    6 )
         clo_CL6_w,         #  closeness centrality (    6 )
         clo_CL18,          # closeness centrality (    18 )
         clo_CL18_w,        #  closeness centrality (    18 )
         betw_CL18)         # betweenness centrality (c   ,     52 )

#    +   ,     
dataset_2 <- df_cleaned %>% 
  select(pop2010to2002_rel,
         Census2002,
         clo,
         clo_w,
         clo_CL6,
         clo_CL6_w,
         clo_CL18,
         clo_CL18_w,
         betw_CL18,
         CL6_centr_betw,    #   (6)  betweenness centrality
         CL18_centr_betw)   #   (18)  betweenness centrality

# V   +    ,     
dataset_3 <- df_cleaned %>% 
  select(pop2010to2002_rel,
         Census2002,
         clo,
         clo_w,
         betw_CL18,
         CL6_variance_2002, #       (6)
         CL6_centr_betw,
         CL6_centr_clo,     #   (6)  closeness centrality
         CL18_variance_2002,#       (18)
         CL18_centr_betw,
         CL18_centr_clo)
